import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'

//pages & components
import Home from './pages/home'
import Signup from './pages/signup'
import Login from './pages/login'
import Navbar from './components/nevbar'

function App() {
    return ( <
        div className = "App" >
        <
        BrowserRouter >
        <
        Navbar / >
        <
        div className = "pages" >
        <
        Routes >
        <
        Route path = "/"
        element = { < Home / > }
        />  <
        Route path = "/signup"
        element = { < Signup / > }
        /> <
        Route path = "/login"
        element = { < Login / > }
        /> <
        /Routes >  <
        /div>     <
        / BrowserRouter >  <
        /div>
    );
}

export default App
